Week 1-2:
Define project requirements
Design database schema
Plan user interface layout
Set up project structure

Week 3-4:
Implement data access objects (DAO) using Hibernate
Set up database connections

Week 5-6:
Design and implement user interface screens
Integrate frontend with backend services
Implement clock in/out functionality

Week 7-8:
Conduct unit tests for backend services
Perform integration testing
Identify and fix bugs

Week 9-10:
Implement additional features such as reporting and customization options
Refactor code for better performance and scalability
Conduct user acceptance testing

Week 11-12:
Deploy the application to a staging environment for final testing
Document installation instructions and user guide
Prepare for production deployment
